<article id="post-2562" class="post-2562 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-rants category-technology tag-apple tag-microsoft tag-patents tag-politics tag-software">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2010/01/greed-kills-innovation/" rel="bookmark">Greed kills innovation</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>I was sitting at my kitchen table, poring over recommendations I&#8217;m writing for my client (partially communicative, partially CYA), when I had one of those sudden thoughts: I need tea.  While I was drinking my tea &#8212; a pomegranate green tea, if you must know &#8212; I had one of those epiphanal moments when something becomes radically clear.<br />
Greed kills innovation.<br />
It&#8217;s short, it&#8217;s simple, it&#8217;s sure to raise the ire of a lot of people, but it&#8217;s also a major problem we&#8217;re seeing lately, especially in internet technologies. It&#8217;s a problem that&#8217;s dogged humanity for generations. And it&#8217;s getting worse.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2010/01/greed-kills-innovation/#more-2562" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Greed kills innovation&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2010/01/greed-kills-innovation/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2010-01-24T22:34:06-07:00">24 January 2010</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/rants/" rel="category tag">Rants</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/technology/" rel="category tag">Technology</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/apple/" rel="tag">apple</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/microsoft/" rel="tag">microsoft</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/patents/" rel="tag">patents</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/politics/" rel="tag">politics</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/software/" rel="tag">software</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2010/01/greed-kills-innovation/#comments">1 Comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Greed kills innovation</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
